How to use.

1. Create DB
   rake db:create

2. Generate Migration
   rake db:new_migration[create_table_name]

3. Edit migration
   add fields.

4. Invoke migration
   rake db:migrate

5. Create Model
   Example:

   # app/models/movie.rb
   #
   class ModelName < ActiveRecord::Base
     validates :title, presence: true
     validates :body, presence: true
   end

6. Run
   $ ruby app/main.rb